column.name: id
note: GWA sample ID for the Genet

column.name: Latitude
note: latitude where the source material was collected

column.name: Longitude
note: longitude where the source material was collected

column.name: Min.per.Tree
note: the amount of time the tree was surveyed for (Density = <Insect>/Min.per.Tree)

column.name: Date
note: date on which the tree was surveyed for insects (confounded with Block, Row, Position)

column.name: PlantingDate
note: date on which the tree was planted from source material

column.name: ALA.all
note: average leaf area of the tree

column.name: SLA.all
note: standardized leaf area of the tree

column.name: BBreakDegDay.all
note: degree days at which the tree’s leaves became fully opened

column.name: EFNMean.all
note: average extra-floral nectaries per leaf of the tree
